high_descs: Turn around and reach the larger sofa.
Pick up the candle from the couch.
Walk towards the right end of the bowl.
Put the candle in the bowl on the couch.
Pick up the bowl from the couch.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelf.
Put the bowl on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the Candle with the Bowl on the Shelf.

high_descs: Turn around from the hall and go to near by to the sofa.
Pick the candle from the sofa.
Take the bowl and turn around near to sofa.
Place the candle in the bowl on the sofa.
Pick the bowl with candle and move around to head some other location.
Take the bowl with candle and head towards the shelf.
Place the bowl and candle on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Pick the candle, bowl from the sofa and place them on the shelf.

high_descs: Walk to a round table on your right and turn right to a sofa.
Pick up a candle from the sofa.
Move right to stand by the right side of the bowl.
Place the ring on the candle on the sofa.
Pick up the bowl from the sofa.
Turn around and walk across the room to the shelf.
Place the bowl on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the candle bowl with a ring inside on the top shelf.
